title: MisterMusic Show 475 - indie, alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 475   [120 minutes]   192kbps MP3 stereo-



New tunes from The National, Weezer, LCD Soundsystem, and Beck on the show this week.
The Oldie of the Week is an alternative rock song that stayed at No.1 on the modern rock chart in the US, for 4 weeks the end of August 1991.  It also was on top of the charts in Australia and New Zealand that summer.

It’s a mix of over 5 decades of indie, alternative and classic hits broadcast weekly, and heard globally on the web- the MisterMusic Show.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

For recorded podcasts of the MisterMusic show, visit his podcast page- 
Shows are updated there first every Sunday.
You can google search mistermusicshow (spelled as one word) and you'll find it.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

MisterMusic is also a presenter on PodCloud1. The website that gives you shorter music segments and themes...easier 
to enjoy in the hectic schedules of today. 
Check it out- PodCloud1 'The One for Great Music'
